Security responsibility: Buyer holds full responsibility for OT network security, firewall configuration, and access control policies. [PRODUCT_NAME] delivers [SECURITY_FEATURES_DELIVERED — e.g., RBAC, audit trail, secure defaults].

Patch management: [SELLER_NAME] recommends regular OS/application patches; scheduling and execution are buyer's responsibility. [SELLER_NAME] is not liable for vulnerabilities arising from unpatched buyer environments.

Liability: [SELLER_NAME]'s liability is limited to [SCOPE_LIMITATION]. No security guarantees are provided for buyer-managed network segments.

Remote access: Remote support requires buyer-provisioned VPN link and signed NDA. [SELLER_NAME] personnel operate within buyer-defined access windows only.
